FBIS4-36041 "drnes107_j_94031" FBIS-NES-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Al-Bid Telephones Syria's al-Asad Al-Bid Telephones Syria's al-Asad EA0206195094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 2 Jun 94 EA0206195094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 2 Jun 94 English BFN [Text] Mr. 'Ali Salim al-Bid, chairman of the Presidential Council, today made a telephone call to the Syrian president, Hafiz al-Asad, and discussed with him the grave situation in the current war in our country and the military escalation by the Sanaa rulers after the Security Council's resolution taken yesterday concerning the situation in our country and the immediate response. He acquainted al-Asad with the bombardment by the Sanaa regime of vital military installations in the capital, Aden, and its desperate attempts to bombard Aden refinery.
